{"tid":1880092,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"19歲男約女網友賞煙火 露宿街頭2天等到「已讀不回」","createTime":"2020-02-14T14:56:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T21:04:56.000Z","uid":34676,"like":587,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"4223d64108b5125266d49573de5327b884f5aa04","tid":1880092,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T14:56:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/3068222?fbclid=IwAR2oj3B9hV4k1z3jo6A7oDykJF3ar-Yq1baCAZeJpzkIEiWdDQS8vugJBpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F3068222%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2oj3B9hV4k1z3jo6A7oDykJF3ar-Yq1baCAZeJpzkIEiWdDQS8vugJBpg&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNnr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=c47f05b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F3068222%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2oj3B9hV4k1z3jo6A7oDykJF3ar-Yq1baCAZeJpzkIEiWdDQS8vugJBpg&h=d0236fc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/3068222?fbclid=IwAR2oj3B9hV4k1z3jo6A7oDykJF3ar-Yq1baCAZeJpzkIEiWdDQS8vugJBpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/02/14/3068222_1_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F02%2F14%2F3068222_1_1.jpg&h=8af4379b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/02/14/3068222_2_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F02%2F14%2F3068222_2_1.jpg&h=61c38c98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔記者洪臣宏／高雄報導〕19歲劉姓男子和女網友相約佛光山賞煙火，滿心以為可以「脫單」，女網友沒有現身，卻要他繼續等待，他露宿街頭2天卻等到「已讀不回」，最後被封鎖「未讀未回」，盤纏用盡劉男身心俱疲走進派出所，暖警資助車費助他返家。<br />\n<br />\n劉男8日深夜1時45分來到大樹分駐所，渾身泥濘且一臉疲憊，他向執勤的員警陳宗豪、李宗祐求助，警方得知她被女網友放鴿子，一起出資1200元讓他坐計程車回家，同時勸他網路騙局多，以此經驗為戒。<br />\n<br />\n原來，在工廠工作的劉男2個月前在網路遊戲上認識1名女網友，2人相約到佛光山看煙火，劉男7日帶了2000元，從台南工廠宿舍搭火車、計程車輾轉到了佛光山，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">到了約定時間，女子沒出現，留訊要他等到凌晨0時，劉男露宿街頭癡癡等待。<br />\n<br />\n隔天，女網友信誓旦旦會跟他會面，到了下午卻「已讀不回」，到了傍晚乾脆封鎖「未讀未回」，劉男此時才驚覺有異，心灰意冷漫步街頭，直到看到大樹分駐所，鼓起勇氣向警方求援。<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n當時火車已經停駛，劉男身上只剩400餘元，不夠計程車車資，陳、李2員湊錢助他返家。劉男心情沉澱之後，日前打電話到大樹分駐所致謝，且說將歸還車資。"},{"pid":"12eb0343cdc8faa5e3dddd83884baf045aa250d0","tid":1880092,"uid":34676,"like":351,"dislike":1,"score":350,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T14:57:50.000Z","msg":"好撚慘啊屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad848e706fe3fcfa57fc751dccec189518d7a405","tid":1880092,"uid":127347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T14:58:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc2bc31dda973ccf90ec74f0cfa345452bc5499","tid":1880092,"uid":168394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T14:58:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0628baa062f57071cd4c10e01a9adc5389b2ae","tid":1880092,"uid":84102,"like":19,"dislike":37,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T14:59:38.000Z","msg":"成個乞兒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfeb57e3f364222987282d844fa9471c722b5796","tid":1880092,"uid":298104,"like":186,"dislike":0,"score":186,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T14:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚慘，但笑左出黎"},{"pid":"3c479d2f59b313eba9a8ac24a22c4e5c7c580275","tid":1880092,"uid":60049,"like":67,"dislike":2,"score":65,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T15:00:29.000Z","msg":"工廠工人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e4cd4e659a9c1b907d438c367092df65256af8","tid":1880092,"uid":214635,"like":273,"dislike":2,"score":271,"citedBy":1,"rep